零温单粒子格林函数, 费曼图技术及其应用

零温单粒子格林函数

薛定谔绘景中引入场算符 $\hat{\psi}{\sigma}(\boldsymbol{r})\hat{\psi}{\sigma}^{\dagger}(\boldsymbol{r})\boldsymbol{r}\sigma\left{\phi_{k}(\boldsymbol{r})\right}k$
\left{\begin{aligned}
\hat{\psi}{\sigma}(\boldsymbol{r}) \equiv \sum{k} \phi_{k}(\boldsymbol{r}) \hat{C}{k \sigma}, \
\hat{\psi}{\sigma}^{\dagger}(\boldsymbol{r}) \equiv \sum_{k} \phi_{k}^*(\boldsymbol{r}) \hat{C}{k \sigma}^{\dagger}.
\end{aligned}\right.
$$
这里只考虑正常态, 不包括超导态、玻色-爱因斯坦凝聚态等复杂状态. 完备基的选择视具体情况而定, 通常可以选择平面波表象、布洛赫表象和瓦尼尔表象, $\hat{C}{k \sigma}^{\dagger}\hat{C}^{}_{k \sigma}$ 则是相应表象下的产生和湮灭算符.

选择布洛赫表象时, 体系有多条能带, 对于费米子通常选择最靠近费米面的能带. 需要强调的是 是全同粒子体系中单体算符的正交完备基，这样的全同粒子体系可能是由实物粒子如电子等组成, 也可能是由非实物粒子如声子等元激发组成. 具体表象下产生湮灭算符间有如下对易关系:
$$
\left[\hat{C}^{}{k \sigma}, \hat{C}{k^{\prime} \sigma^{\prime}}^{\dagger}\right]{\mp}=\delta{k k^{\prime}} \delta_{\sigma \sigma^{\prime}}, \quad\left[\hat{C}{k \sigma}, \hat{C}{k^{\prime} \sigma^{\prime}}\right]{\mp}=\left[\hat{C}{k \sigma}^{\dagger}, \hat{C}{k^{\prime} \sigma^{\prime}}^{\dagger}\right]{\mp}=0,

\left[\hat{\psi}^{}{\sigma}(\boldsymbol{x}), \hat{\psi}{\sigma^{\prime}}^{\dagger}\left(\boldsymbol{x}^{\prime}\right)\right]{\mp}=\delta\left(\boldsymbol{x}-\boldsymbol{x}^{\prime}\right) \delta{\sigma \sigma^{\prime}},

\left[\hat{\psi}{\sigma}(\boldsymbol{x}), \hat{\psi}{\sigma^{\prime}}\left(\boldsymbol{x}^{\prime}\right)\right]{\mp}=\left[\hat{\psi}{\sigma}^{\dagger}(\boldsymbol{x}), \hat{\psi}{\sigma^{\prime}}^{\dagger}\left(\boldsymbol{x}^{\prime}\right)\right]{\mp}=0 .
$$
利用海森伯绘景和薛定谔绘景中算符的变换关系, 可以得到海森伯绘景下场算符 $\hat{\psi}{H \sigma}(\boldsymbol{x}, t)\hat{\psi}{\sigma}(\boldsymbol{x})$
\hat{\psi}{H \sigma}(\boldsymbol{x}, t)=\mathrm{e}^{\mathrm{i} \hat{H} t} \hat{\psi}{\sigma}(\boldsymbol{x}) \mathrm{e}^{-\mathrm{i} \hat{H} t},
$$
这里的哈密顿量不显含时间.

零温单粒子格林函数的定义

零温单粒子格林函数
$$
G_{\alpha \beta}\left(\boldsymbol{x}, t ; \boldsymbol{x}^{\prime}, t^{\prime}\right) \equiv-\mathrm{i}\left\langle\psi_{H}^{0}\left|\hat{T}\left[\hat{\psi}^{}{H \alpha}(\boldsymbol{x}, t) \hat{\psi}{H \beta}^{\dagger}\left(\boldsymbol{x}^{\prime}, t^{\prime}\right)\right]\right| \psi_{H}^{0}\right\rangle .
$$
有文献也称这种形式的格林函数为因果格林函数, 它是最常用的格林函数, 可以用图形技术来处理. 由于格林函数 中含有两个时间, 一般地我们也称其为双时格林函数. 对于热力学因果格林函数来说, 它的物理意义是在 个粒子的统计系综中, 在 时刻 位置处产生一个粒子, 它运动到 时刻在 处湮灭的传播概率. 这第 个粒子与 个粒子是有 相互作用的. 如果有外场, 或者相互作用与自旋有关, 粒子在运动过程中由于受到散射或外场作用, 自旋可能会改变. 由于相互作用的存在, 该运动粒子与 裸粒子(即无相互作用时)的能谱会不同. 我们将这样的粒子称为准粒子, 它的能谱由格林函数的极点确定.
当时间 时, 格林函数表明先湮灭一个粒子然后再产生它, 这完全遵守因果关系. 零温的因果格林函数则表示在 个粒子的基态中产生再湮灭一个粒子的传播概率幅.

格林函数的极点是粒子的能量, 亦即哈密顿量的本征值. 一般来说本征值是实数. 但由于现在产生的是准粒子, 准粒子在运动过程中由于与其他粒子的相互作用, 可能会衰变. 所以准粒子是有寿命的, 这一点在格林函数上表示为极点是个复数. 实部表示准粒子的能量, 虚部的倒数是准粒子的寿命. 当粒子不衰变时, 虚部是无穷小量, 寿命无限长.

这里的 与我们之前定义的 同为基态, 这样表示是为了强调式中所有物理量都在海森伯绘景中.

的本征值方程是

引入编时算符 , 定义为
$$
\begin{aligned}
\hat{T}\left[\hat{A}{H}(t) \hat{B}{H}\left(t^{\prime}\right)\right]&=\left{\begin{aligned}
&\hat{A}{H}(t) \hat{B}{H}\left(t^{\prime}\right), &t>t^{\prime}, \
&\pm \hat{B}{H}\left(t^{\prime}\right) \hat{A}{H}(t), &t<t^{\prime}
\end{aligned}\right.\
&=\theta(t-t^\prime)\hat{A}{H}(t) \hat{B}{H}\left(t^{\prime}\right)\pm\theta(t^\prime-t)\hat{B}{H}\left(t^{\prime} \right)\hat{A}{H}(t),
\end{aligned}

\hat{T}\left[\hat{A}(t) \hat{B}\left(t^{\prime}\right)\right]=\hat{T}\left[\pm \hat{B}\left(t^{\prime}\right) \hat{A}(t)\right].
$$

对称性质

零温单粒子格林函数在有对称性的体系下, 形式可以简化, 具体体现在其所依赖的参量减少:

  1. 不显含时间, 具有时间对称性

  2. 空间均匀 $([\hat{H}, \hat{P}]-=0)$
    G    {\alpha \beta}\left(\boldsymbol{x}, t ; \boldsymbol{x}^{\prime}, t^{\prime}\right)=G_{\alpha \beta}\left(\boldsymbol{x}-\boldsymbol{x}^{\prime} ; t, t^{\prime}\right) .
    $$

  3. 相互作用与自旋无关

    其中

  4. 具备以上三个对称性

物理意义

假设 , 将场算符化为在薛定谔绘景下的表示:
$$
\begin{aligned}
G_{\alpha \beta}\left(\boldsymbol{x}, t ; \boldsymbol{x}^{\prime}, t^{\prime}\right) &=-\mathrm{i}\left\langle\psi_{H}^{0}\left|\hat{\psi}^{}{H \alpha}(\boldsymbol{x}, t) \hat{\psi}{H \beta}^{\dagger}\left(\boldsymbol{x}^{\prime}, t^{\prime}\right)\right| \psi_{H}^{0}\right\rangle\
&=-\mathrm{i}\left\langle\psi_{H}^{0}\left|\mathrm{e}^{\mathrm{i} \hat{H} t}\hat{\psi}^{}{\alpha}(\boldsymbol{x})\mathrm{e}^{-\mathrm{i} \hat{H} t}\mathrm{e}^{\mathrm{i} \hat{H} t^{\prime}} \hat{\psi}{\beta}^{\dagger}\left(\boldsymbol{x}^{\prime}\right)\mathrm{e}^{-\mathrm{i} \hat{H} t^{\prime}}\right| \psi_{H}^{0}\right\rangle \
&=-\mathrm{i} \mathrm{e}^{\mathrm{i} E_{g}\left(t-t^{\prime}\right)}\left\langle\psi_{H}^{0}\left|\hat{\psi}^{}{\alpha}(\boldsymbol{x}) \mathrm{e}^{-\mathrm{i}\hat{H}\left(t-t^{\prime}\right)} \hat{\psi}{\beta}^{\dagger}\left(\boldsymbol{x}^{\prime}\right)\right| \psi_{H}^{0}\right\rangle .
\end{aligned}
$$
这样, 零温单粒子格林函数的物理意义便是: 时刻基态中 位置产生一个自旋为 的粒子, 然后经过 的演化在 时刻这一粒子在 处且自旋为 消灭的几率幅.

物理量的表示

单体算符的基态平均

单体算符可以利用场算符写为(二次量子化):
$$
\hat{F}^{(1)}=\sum_{\alpha \beta} \int \hat{\psi}{\alpha}^{\dagger}(\boldsymbol{x}) \hat{f}^{}{\alpha \beta}(\boldsymbol{x}) \hat{\psi}^{}{\beta}(\boldsymbol{x}) \mathrm{d} \boldsymbol{x} ,

\begin{aligned}
\left\langle\psi{H}^{0}\left|\hat{F}^{(1)}\right| \psi_{H}^{0}\right\rangle &=\sum_{\alpha \beta} \int \mathrm{d} \boldsymbol{x}\left\langle\psi_{H}^{0}\left|\hat{\psi}{\alpha}^{\dagger}(\boldsymbol{x}) \hat{f}^{}{\alpha \beta}(\boldsymbol{x}) \hat{\psi}^{}{\beta}(\boldsymbol{x})\right| \psi{H}^{0}\right\rangle \
&=\sum_{\alpha \beta} \int \mathrm{d} \boldsymbol{x} \lim {\boldsymbol{x}^{\prime} \rightarrow \boldsymbol{x}} \hat{f}{\alpha \beta}(\boldsymbol{x})\left\langle\psi_{H}^{0}\left|\hat{\psi}{\alpha}^{\dagger}\left(\boldsymbol{x}^{\prime}\right) \hat{\psi}^{}{\beta}(\boldsymbol{x})\right| \psi_{H}^{0}\right\rangle ,
\end{aligned}
$$
注意这里 $\hat{f}{\alpha \beta}(\boldsymbol{x})\boldsymbol{x}$
\begin{aligned}
&\left\langle\psi{H}^{0}\left|\hat{F}^{(1)}\right| \psi_{H}^{0}\right\rangle\
=&\sum_{\alpha \beta} \int \mathrm{d} \boldsymbol{x} \lim {\boldsymbol{x}^{\prime} \rightarrow \boldsymbol{x}} \hat{f}{\alpha \beta}(\boldsymbol{x})\left\langle\psi_{H}^{0}\left| \mathrm{e}^{\mathrm{i} \hat{H} t} \hat{\psi}{H \alpha}^{\dagger}\left(\boldsymbol{x}^{\prime}\right)\mathrm{e}^{-\mathrm{i} \hat{H} t} \mathrm{e}^{\mathrm{i} \hat{H} t} \hat{\psi}^{}{H \beta}(\boldsymbol{x}) \mathrm{e}^{-\mathrm{i} \hat{H} t} \right| \psi_{H}^{0}\right\rangle\
=&\sum_{\alpha \beta} \int \mathrm{d} \boldsymbol{x} \lim {\boldsymbol{x}^{\prime} \rightarrow \boldsymbol{x}} \hat{f}{\alpha \beta}(\boldsymbol{x})\left\langle\psi_{H}^{0}\left|\hat{\psi}{H \alpha}^{\dagger}\left(\boldsymbol{x}^{\prime}, t\right) \hat{\psi}^{}{H \beta}(\boldsymbol{x}, t)\right| \psi_{H}^{0}\right\rangle .
\end{aligned}

\begin{aligned}
&\left\langle\psi_{H}^{0}\left|\hat{F}^{(1)}\right| \psi_{H}^{0}\right\rangle \
=&\sum_{\alpha \beta} \int \mathrm{d} \boldsymbol{x} \lim_{t’\to t^+\atop\boldsymbol{x}’\to \boldsymbol{x}} \hat{f}{\alpha \beta}(\boldsymbol{x})\left\langle\psi{H}^{0}\left|\hat{\psi}{H \alpha}^{\dagger}\left(\boldsymbol{x}^{\prime}, t^{\prime}\right) \hat{\psi}^{}{H \beta}(\boldsymbol{x}, t)\right| \psi_{H}^{0}\right\rangle \
=&\sum_{\alpha \beta} \int \mathrm{d} \boldsymbol{x} \lim_{t’\to t^+\atop\boldsymbol{x}’\to \boldsymbol{x}} \hat{f}{\alpha \beta}(\boldsymbol{x})\left\langle\psi{H}^{0}\left|\hat{T}\left[\hat{\psi}{H \alpha}^{\dagger}\left(\boldsymbol{x}^{\prime}, t^{\prime}\right) \hat{\psi}^{}{H \beta}(\boldsymbol{x}, t)\right]\right| \psi_{H}^{0}\right\rangle \
=&\pm \sum_{\alpha \beta} \int \mathrm{d} \boldsymbol{x} \lim_{t’\to t^+\atop\boldsymbol{x}’\to \boldsymbol{x}} \hat{f}{\alpha \beta}(\boldsymbol{x})\left\langle\psi{H}^{0}\left|\hat{T}\left[\hat{\psi}^{}{H \beta}(\boldsymbol{x}, t) \hat{\psi}{H \alpha}^{\dagger}\left(\boldsymbol{x}^{\prime}, t^{\prime}\right)\right]\right| \psi_{H}^{0}\right\rangle \
=&\pm \mathrm{i} \sum_{\alpha \beta} \int \mathrm{d} \boldsymbol{x} \lim_{t’\to t^+\atop\boldsymbol{x}’\to \boldsymbol{x}} \hat{f}{\alpha \beta}(\boldsymbol{x}) G{\beta \alpha}\left(\boldsymbol{x}, t ; \boldsymbol{x}^{\prime}, t^{\prime}\right) .\end{aligned}
$$
总动能算符的基态平均.
总动能算符是单体算符, 可以写为:
$$
\hat{T}{K}=\sum{\alpha} \int \hat{\psi}{\alpha}^{\dagger}(\boldsymbol{x})\left(-\frac{\nabla^{2}}{2 m}\right) \hat{\psi}^{}{\alpha}(\boldsymbol{x}) \mathrm{d} \boldsymbol{x},

\hat{f}{\alpha \beta}(\boldsymbol{x})=-\frac{\nabla^{2}}{2 m} \delta{\alpha \beta} .

\begin{aligned}
\left\langle\psi_{H}^{0}\left|\hat{T}{K}\right| \psi{H}^{0}\right\rangle&=\pm \mathrm{i} \sum_{\alpha\beta} \int \mathrm{d} \boldsymbol{x} \lim_{t’\to t^+\atop\boldsymbol{x}’\to \boldsymbol{x}} \left(-\frac{\nabla^{2}}{2 m}\delta_{\alpha \beta}\right) G_{\beta \alpha}\left(\boldsymbol{x}, t ; \boldsymbol{x}^{\prime}, t^{\prime}\right)\
&=\pm \mathrm{i} \sum_{\alpha} \int \mathrm{d} \boldsymbol{x} \lim_{t’\to t^+\atop\boldsymbol{x}’\to \boldsymbol{x}} \left(-\frac{\nabla^{2}}{2 m}\right) G_{\alpha \alpha}\left(\boldsymbol{x}, t ; \boldsymbol{x}^{\prime}, t^{\prime}\right).
\end{aligned}
$$

基态能(两种方法求解)

(i) 方法之一
全同费米子体系的哈密顿量是
$$
\hat{H}=\hat{T}{K}+\hat{V},

\begin{aligned} \hat{T}{K}&=\sum_{\sigma}\int\mathrm{d}\boldsymbol{x}\hat{\psi}\sigma^\dagger(\boldsymbol{x})\left( -\frac{\nabla^2}{2m} \right) \hat{\psi}\sigma(\boldsymbol{x}),\
\hat{V}&=\frac{1}{2}\sum_\alpha\sum_\beta\iint\mathrm{d}\boldsymbol{x}\mathrm{d}\boldsymbol{x}’\hat{\psi}\alpha^\dagger(\boldsymbol{x})\psi_\beta^\dagger(\boldsymbol{x}’)\hat{V}(|\boldsymbol{x}-\boldsymbol{x}’|)\hat{\psi}{\beta}^{ }(\boldsymbol{x}’)\hat{\psi}\alpha^{ }(\boldsymbol{x}).
\end{aligned}

E_g=\left\langle \psi_H^0\left|\hat{H}\right|\psi_H^0 \right\rangle=\left\langle \psi_H^0\left|\hat{T}k\right|\psi_H^0 \right\rangle+\left\langle\psi_H^0\left| \hat{V} \right| \psi_H^0 \right\rangle,

\left\langle \psi_H^0 \left| \hat{T}{K} \right| \psi_H^0\right\rangle=-\mathrm{i}\sum_\sigma\int\mathrm{d}\boldsymbol{x}\lim{t’\to t^+\atop\boldsymbol{x}’\to \boldsymbol{x}}\left( -\frac{\nabla^2}{2m} \right) G{\sigma\sigma}(\boldsymbol{x},t;\boldsymbol{x}’,t’),

\mathrm{i}\frac{\partial}{\partial t}\hat{\psi}{H\alpha}(\boldsymbol{x},t)=\left[ \hat\psi_{H\alpha}(\boldsymbol{x},t),\hat{H} \right]-,

\left[ \hat{\psi}{H\alpha},\hat{H} \right]-=\mathrm{e}^{\mathrm{i}\hat{H}t}\left[ \hat{\psi}\alpha(\boldsymbol{x}),\hat{H} \right]-\mathrm{e}^{-\mathrm{i}\hat{H}t},

\left[ \hat\psi_\alpha(\boldsymbol{x}),\hat{H} \right]-=\left( -\frac{\nabla^2}{2m} \right)\hat{\psi}_\alpha(\boldsymbol{x})+\sum_\sigma\int\mathrm{d}\boldsymbol{z}’ \hat{\psi}_\sigma^\dagger(\boldsymbol{z}’) \hat{V}(\boldsymbol{x},\boldsymbol{z}’)\hat{\psi}_\sigma(\boldsymbol{z’})\hat{\psi}_\alpha(\boldsymbol{x}).
$$

练习: 证明上式成立.

代回运动方程, 得到

对等式两边左乘 然后取基态平均, 得到
$$
\begin{aligned}
&\left\langle \psi_H^0\left| \hat\psi_{H\alpha}^\dagger(\boldsymbol{x}’,t’)\left( \mathrm{i}\frac{\partial}{\partial t}+\frac{\nabla^2}{2m}\right)\hat\psi_{H\alpha}(\boldsymbol{x},t) \right|\psi_H^0 \right\rangle\
=&\left\langle \psi_H^0\left|\sum_\sigma\int\mathrm{d}\boldsymbol{z}’\hat\psi_{H\alpha}^\dagger(\boldsymbol{x}’,t’)\hat{\psi}{H\sigma}^\dagger(\boldsymbol{z}’,t)\hat{V}(\boldsymbol{x},\boldsymbol{z}’) \hat\psi{H\sigma}(\boldsymbol{z}’,t)\hat\psi_{H\alpha}(\boldsymbol{x},t)\right|\psi_H^0\right\rangle,
\end{aligned}

\begin{aligned}
&\lim_{t’\to t^+\atop\boldsymbol{x}’\to \boldsymbol{x}}\left\langle \psi_H^0\left| \sum_{\alpha}\int\mathrm{d}\boldsymbol{x}\hat\psi_{H\alpha}^\dagger(\boldsymbol{x}’,t’)\left( \mathrm{i}\frac{\partial}{\partial t}+\frac{\nabla^2}{2m} \right)\hat\psi_{H\alpha}(\boldsymbol{x},t)\right|\psi_H^0 \right\rangle\
=&\lim_{t’\to t^+\atop\boldsymbol{x}’\to \boldsymbol{x}}\left\langle \psi_H^0\left| \sum_\alpha\sum_\sigma\int\mathrm{d}\boldsymbol{x}\int\mathrm{d}\boldsymbol{z}’\hat\psi_{H\alpha}^\dagger(\boldsymbol{x}’,t)\hat\psi_{H\sigma}^\dagger(\boldsymbol{z}’,t)\right.\right.\
&\left.\left.\qquad\qquad\qquad\qquad\times\hat{V}(\boldsymbol{x},\boldsymbol{z}’)\hat\psi_{H\sigma}(\boldsymbol{z}’,t)\hat{\psi}{H\alpha}(\boldsymbol{x},t) \right|\psi_H^0 \right\rangle.
\end{aligned}

-\mathrm{i}\sum_\alpha\int\mathrm{d}\boldsymbol{x}\lim{t’\to t^+\atop\boldsymbol{x}’\to \boldsymbol{x}}\left( \mathrm{i}\frac{\partial}{\partial t}+\frac{\nabla^2}{2m} \right) G_{\alpha\alpha}(\boldsymbol{x},t;\boldsymbol{x}’,t’),

\left\langle \psi_H^0\left|\sum_\alpha\sum_\sigma\int\mathrm{d}\boldsymbol{x}\int\mathrm{d}\boldsymbol{z}’\hat{\psi}{H\alpha}^\dagger(\boldsymbol{x},t)\hat\psi{H\sigma}^\dagger(\boldsymbol{z}’,t)\hat{V}(\boldsymbol{x},\boldsymbol{z}’)\hat{\psi}{H\sigma}(\boldsymbol{z}’,t)\hat{\psi}{H\alpha}(\boldsymbol{x},t)\right|\psi_H^0 \right\rangle.

\hat\psi_{H\alpha}(\boldsymbol{x},t)=\mathrm{e}^{\mathrm{i}\hat{H}t}\hat\psi_\alpha(\boldsymbol{x})\mathrm{e}^{-\mathrm{i}\hat{H}t},

\left\langle \psi_H^0\left|\sum_\alpha\sum_\sigma\int\mathrm{d}\boldsymbol{x}\int\mathrm{d}\boldsymbol{z}’\hat{\psi}\alpha^\dagger(\boldsymbol{x})\hat\psi_\sigma^\dagger(\boldsymbol{z}’)\hat{V}(\boldsymbol{x},\boldsymbol{z}’)\hat{\psi}\sigma(\boldsymbol{z}’)\hat\psi_\alpha(\boldsymbol{x})\right|\psi_H^0\right\rangle=2\left\langle\psi_H^0\left|\hat{V}\right|\psi_H^0\right\rangle.

\left\langle \psi_H^0\left|\hat{V}\right|\psi_H^0 \right\rangle=-\frac{\mathrm{i}}{2}\sum{\alpha}\int\mathrm{d} \boldsymbol{x}\lim{t’\to t^+\atop\boldsymbol{x}’\to \boldsymbol{x}}\left( \mathrm{i}\frac{\partial}{\partial t}+\frac{\nabla^2}{2m} \right) G_{\alpha\alpha}(\boldsymbol{x},t;\boldsymbol{x}’,t’).

\begin{aligned}
E_g=&\left\langle \psi_H^0\left|\hat{T}k\right|\psi_H^0 \right\rangle+\left\langle\psi_H^0\left|\hat{V}\right|\psi_H^0\right\rangle \
=&-\mathrm{i}\sum_\alpha\int\mathrm{d}\boldsymbol{x}\lim{t’\to t^+\atop\boldsymbol{x}’\to \boldsymbol{x}}\left( -\frac{\nabla^2}{2m} \right) G_{\alpha\alpha}(\boldsymbol{x},t;\boldsymbol{x}’,t’) \
&-\frac{\mathrm{i}}{2}\sum_\alpha\int\mathrm{d}\boldsymbol{x}\lim_{t’\to t^+\atop\boldsymbol{x}’\to \boldsymbol{x}}\left( \mathrm{i}\frac{\partial}{\partial t}+\frac{\nabla^2}{2m} \right) G_{\alpha\alpha}(\boldsymbol{x},t;\boldsymbol{x}’,t’) \
=&-\frac{\mathrm{i}}{2}\sum_\alpha \int\mathrm{d}\boldsymbol{x}\lim_{t’\to t^+\atop\boldsymbol{x}’\to \boldsymbol{x}}\left( \mathrm{i}\frac{\partial}{\partial t}-\frac{\nabla^2}{2m} \right) G_{\alpha\alpha}(\boldsymbol{x},t;\boldsymbol{x}’,t’).\end{aligned}
$$
(ii) 方法之二(利用 Hellmann-Feynmann 定理)
首先构造含有参量 的哈密顿量
$$
\hat{H}(\lambda)\equiv \hat{T}K+\lambda\hat{V},\quad (0\le \lambda\le 1)

\hat{H}(\lambda=1)=\hat{H},\quad \hat{H}(\lambda=0)=\hat{T}K.

\hat{H}(\lambda)\left|\psi_H^0(\lambda)\right\rangle=E_g(\lambda)\left| \psi_H^0(\lambda) \right\rangle,

E_g(\lambda=1)=E_g,\quad E_g(\lambda=0)=E_g^0,\quad \left\langle\psi_H^0(\lambda)\right|\left.\psi_H^0(\lambda)\right\rangle=1.

E_g(\lambda)=\left\langle\psi_H^0(\lambda)\left|\hat{H}(\lambda)\right|\psi_H^0(\lambda)\right\rangle,



\frac{\mathrm{d}}{\mathrm{d}\lambda}E_g(\lambda)=\frac{1}{\lambda}\left\langle\psi_H^0(\lambda)\right|\lambda\hat{V}\left|\psi_H^0(\lambda)\right\rangle,

\begin{aligned}
\int_0^1\mathrm{d}\lambda\frac{\mathrm{d}}{\mathrm{d}\lambda}E_g(\lambda)=&\int_0^1\mathrm{d}\lambda\frac{1}{\lambda}\left\langle\psi_H^0(\lambda)\right|\lambda\hat{V}\left|\psi_H^0(\lambda)\right\rangle\
\Rightarrow E_g(\lambda)\Biggr|0^1=&\int_0^1\mathrm{d}\lambda\frac{1}{\lambda}\underbrace{\left\langle\psi_H^0(\lambda)\right|\lambda\hat{V}\left|\psi_H^0(\lambda)\right\rangle}{\text{系统相互作用的基态平均值.}},
\end{aligned}

\begin{aligned}
E_g(\lambda)&=E_g^0+\int_0^1\mathrm{d}\lambda\frac{1}{\lambda}\left\langle\psi_H^0(\lambda)\right|\lambda\hat{V}\left|\psi_H^0(\lambda)\right\rangle\
&=E_g^0+\int_0^1\frac{\mathrm{d}\lambda}{\lambda}\left[ -\frac{\mathrm{i}}{2}\int\mathrm{d}\boldsymbol{x}\lim{t’\to t^+\atop\boldsymbol{x}’\to \boldsymbol{x}}\left( \mathrm{i}\frac{\partial}{\partial t}+\frac{\nabla^2}{2m} \right) G{\alpha\alpha}(\boldsymbol{x},t;\boldsymbol{x}’,t’;\lambda) \right].
\end{aligned}
$$
这样就得到了基态能的第二种表达式.
自由粒子系统的基态能 的计算.
哈密顿量用场算符表示为
$$
\hat{H}=\hat{T}K=\sum_\sigma\int\hat\psi_\sigma^\dagger(\boldsymbol{x})\left( -\frac{\nabla^2}{2m} \right)\hat\psi_\sigma(\boldsymbol{x})\mathrm{d}\boldsymbol{x}.

\hat{\psi}\sigma(\boldsymbol{x})=\frac{1}{\sqrt{V}}\sum_k\mathrm{e}^{\mathrm{i}\boldsymbol{k}\cdot\boldsymbol{x}}\hat{C}{k\sigma},\quad\hat\psi_\sigma^\dagger(\boldsymbol{x})=\frac{1}{\sqrt{V}}\sum_k\mathrm{e}^{-\mathrm{i}\boldsymbol{k}\cdot\boldsymbol{x}}\hat{C}{k\sigma}^\dagger.

\hat{H}=\hat{T}K=\sum{k,\sigma}\epsilon_k^0\hat{C}{k\sigma}^\dagger\hat{C}{k\sigma}^{ },\quad\left( \epsilon_k^0\equiv\frac{k^2}{2m} \right)

\left|\Phi^0\right\rangle=\prod_{|\boldsymbol k|\le k_{\mathrm{F}}\atop\sigma}\hat{C}{k\sigma}^\dagger|0\rangle,

\langle 0|0\rangle =\mathbf{1},\quad\hat{C}{k\sigma}|0\rangle=0.

\begin{aligned}
